title: Episode 264: Like Riding a Bike (Feat. Gizelle Bryant)
itunes:title: Episode 264: Like Riding a Bike (Feat. Gizelle Bryant)
description:
Gizelle Bryant, star of the Real Housewives of Potomac, opens up about the reconciliation with her ex-husband. Gizelle shares a hilarious story about how she got caught cheating back when she was in college, she dishes on her friends partners hitting on her, and much more. Enjoy!
